# Multilingual Text Preprocessing Engine

A modular NLP system built with **FastAPI + Docker** that supports **English and Arabic text preprocessing** with a configurable pipeline and web-based GUI.

---

## 🚀 Features

### English NLP
- Tokenization
- Stopword removal
- Stemming (Porter Stemmer)
- Lemmatization (WordNet)
- Regex cleaning

### Arabic NLP
- Tashkeel removal
- Tatweel removal
- Alef/Hamza normalization
- Stopword removal
- Stemming (ISRI Stemmer)

### System Features
- Dynamic preprocessing pipeline
- Language detection & validation
- REST API (FastAPI)
- Web GUI (HTML/CSS/JS)
- Fully Dockerized (single container)

