## ⚙️ Installation (Local)

### 1. Clone Project
```bash
git clone <repo-url>
cd text-preprocessor
2. Create Virtual Environment
python -m venv venv
3. Activate Environment

Windows:

venv\Scripts\activate

Mac/Linux:

source venv/bin/activate
4. Install Dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
5. Run Application
uvicorn src.main:app --reload
🌐 Run in Browser
GUI:
http://127.0.0.1:8000/
API Docs (Swagger):
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs
🐳 Docker Deployment (Recommended)
1. Build Image
docker build -t text-preprocessor .
2. Run Container
docker run -p 8000:8000 text-preprocessor
3. Access App

GUI:

http://localhost:8000/

API:

http://localhost:8000/docs
📡 API Usage
Endpoint:
POST /preprocess
Request Example:
{
  "text": "Hello world! Welcome to AI.",
  "language": "english",
  "remove_stopwords": true,
  "stemming": true,
  "lemmatization": false,
  "normalization": true
}
Response Example:
{
  "original_text": "Hello world! Welcome to AI.",
  "processed_text": "hello world welcom ai",
  "language": "english",
  "applied_steps": {
    "remove_stopwords": true,
    "stemming": true,
    "lemmatization": false,
    "normalization": true
  },
  "success": true,
  "message": "Text preprocessing completed successfully."
}
